            "answer_text": "Michael Jackson was not all that of a punch bag for everyone. All the Jackson's said that Michael was the only one that fought back his father when he was beating them or him. In later years, Michael became a gentle soul , shy, soft spoken and barely vocal because most likely Michael became more spiritual. In Michael Jackson's early twenties and in his thirties, he couldn't control jealousy much when it came to his girlfriend. He would throw and break things. He got out of control with jealousy just like any normal bloke. Not liking his girlfriend to dance three sets with any man even a male friend. Once Chris Tucker was dancing with his girlfriend and after two sets, Michael got mad and snatched her away from Chris. In 1986, Michael destroyed a brand new car with a baseball bat when his girlfriend told him that she no longer loved him. She didn't mean it. He had cheated and she found out. The damage was done. The car was unrepairable. There are several hotels that Michael Jackson was thrown out off for breaking up the entire room. One in Barbados , one in Caracas, Venezuela, and Michael broke up a house in Las Vegas unnecessarily when he thought his girlfriend had left him again in 2008. You can Google it. \u201c Michael Jackson owes landlord for destroying property in Las Vegas. Did Michael shout? Yes, and when he did, it was not the sweet voice but a scary, terrifying voice. Did Michael yell regularly, NO! Michael tried not to shout at anyone but there were times it became necessary. There is a YouTube video of Michael being very much in command verbally to one girl who was practising the walk for ' The Way You Make Me Feel.' You can hear him telling her to work the stage. I never heard Michael Jackson curse and say the F word. Maybe he respected me, to not curse in my presence. I have cursed around him out of anger. Michael would say, it's not becoming of you to curse! I would say, you pissed me off enough to make me curse. Michael Jackson would say because I never heard you do it before, don't again! If, Michael Jackson cursed to Lisa Marie Presley ,then he had no respect for her as a woman. I know Lisa Marie Presley curse like it's part of her vocabulary. Maybe her swearing rubbed off on him. I don't know what happened with her claiming he cursed, because he never did around me as I said. Michael was also a Jehovah Witness brought up in this religion. Cursing was considered a grave sin! I believe Lisa Marie Presley lied that Michael use to curse in front of her. Or it could be she just wanted to say he was a regular guy that did regular things, like curse\u2026it could have been a slip of the tongue. I have seen the very best in Michael Jackson but I have also seen the worst with his jealousy. Throwing vases, lampshades, plates, chairs, anything he could get his hands on. Never at anyone just at walls to get rid of rage! Michael Jackson was a lover, not a fighter! Michael Jackson was a giver not a taker! My daughter gave Michael Jackson a gift once and he cried. He cried because people always wanted from him. No one ever gave to him! The gesture of giving him a gift who had everything , and she was a young girl touched him deeply. Michael Jackson is true to himself! True to others, black ,white, Chinese, Indian it didn't matter to him about race! Michael loved and cared for all. He was way beyond his time. Maybe mankind will get there some time! Michael Jackson lived for the love and gratification of God. Hence why he could not have hurt any child! He was a victim of fraud that was sanctioned by white justice on a black man. Michael Jackson said that he learnt not to trust but he didn\u2019t have the personality and spirit to live a life being forever suspicious. It took too much energy, and hence why the Arvizos caught him off guard! He had love for the dying child Garvin. But Garvin's greedy mother had no love for her son, only desire for riches that was gained wrongfully. Mrs. Arvizo suffered from illusions of grandeur after an underprivileged existence. Michael Jackson is from a higher realm. One filled with love not hate! An angel from heaven! Angels from heaven get mad, they get angry when they witness the evil souls of man. The length they will go for material gain. The killings, lying, exploits , conniving, dangerous traits of mankind. Michael is one angel that gets angry and have burst of temper at times. ",
